{"totalPage": 1, "totalElement": 13, "content": [{"id": 45, "createdAt": "2022-06-14T09:53:08", "updatedAt": "2025-01-16T05:30:52", "langCode": "zh", "appName": "Routines", "shortDescription": "根据具体情况，帮助您自动执行重复任务。", "pkgName": "com.samsung.android.app.routine2", "thumbnails": [], "title": "", "description": "", "minLevel": 0, "maxLevel": 10000, "category": "lifeup", "priority": 0, "postState": 1, "tags": "触摸"}, {"id": 49, "createdAt": "2022-06-14T09:55:56", "updatedAt": "2025-01-16T05:33:09", "langCode": "zh", "appName": "Nice Shot", "shortDescription": "更方便地使用屏幕截图和屏幕录制功能。在截屏后，您可以立即删除截图，无需保存，而在录制屏幕时，您不会受到通知、信息或声音等的干扰。", "pkgName": "com.samsung.android.app.captureplugin", "thumbnails": ["https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-2851c4.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-39c619.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-68d3bb.png"], "title": "尝试更强大的屏幕截图和屏幕录制功能。", "description": "- 删除屏幕截图工具栏上提供的按钮\n- 不要将所截取的图片复制到剪贴板\n- 提供各种自拍视频选项\n- 在屏幕录制期间开启免打扰", "minLevel": 0, "maxLevel": 10000, "category": "lifeup", "priority": 0, "postState": 1, "tags": "功能扩展"}, {"id": 50, "createdAt": "2022-06-14T09:56:36", "updatedAt": "2025-01-16T05:30:37", "langCode": "zh", "appName": "Sound Assistant", "shortDescription": "扩展音频系统设置，增加便利性", "pkgName": "com.samsung.android.soundassistant", "thumbnails": ["https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-245839.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-31df0c.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-562174.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-681e76.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-889987.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-97318d.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-b6ce94.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-e9b5d6.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-f21f32.png"], "title": "扩展音频系统设置，增加便利性", "description": "- 按照应用程序有各种音量控制\n- 150 级详细的音量控制\n- 支持应用程序同时播放声音 \n- 使用您的音量控制面板自定义布局\n- 向音量控制面板添加颜色\n- 通过音量按钮控制播放或媒体音量\n- 使用媒体应用程序收藏设置，快速访问媒体应用程序\n- 蓝牙连接后播放视频时同步声音\n- 为铃声或通知新建振动模式\n- 保存并分享您自己的 EQ 设置", "minLevel": 0, "maxLevel": 10000, "category": "lifeup", "priority": 0, "postState": 1, "tags": "功能扩展"}, {"id": 51, "createdAt": "2022-06-14T09:57:16", "updatedAt": "2025-01-16T05:36:20", "langCode": "zh", "appName": "NotiStar", "shortDescription": "轻松管理通知历史记录", "pkgName": "com.samsung.systemui.notilus", "thumbnails": ["https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2025-01-10-1841d8.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2025-01-10-5e568a.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2025-01-10-8a566a.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2025-01-10-a11557.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2025-01-10-a5dd59.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2025-01-10-cf1d75.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2025-01-10-ee302f.png"], "title": "新通知管理服务", "description": "- 选择应用程序以保存通知\n- 新建一个页面，让您可以检查包含所选关键词的通知\n- 按关键词搜索您需要的通知\n- 通过锁定屏幕上的快捷方式图标，快速检查通知历史记录\n- 更改锁定屏幕快捷方式图标的位置和颜色\n- 配置存储通知的期限", "minLevel": 0, "maxLevel": 10000, "category": "lifeup", "priority": 0, "postState": 1, "tags": "锁定屏幕;通知"}, {"id": 52, "createdAt": "2022-06-14T09:57:50", "updatedAt": "2025-01-16T05:30:05", "langCode": "zh", "appName": "Edge Touch", "shortDescription": "轻松调整侧屏幕触控设置", "pkgName": "com.samsung.android.app.edgetouch", "thumbnails": ["https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-995865.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-a28c20.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-bfb222.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-cde424.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-e40938.png"], "title": "轻松调整侧屏幕触控设置", "description": "- 防止意外的侧屏幕触控\n- 轻松管理侧屏幕区域\n- 提供了不会识别长按的抓握区域\n- 单独管理侧屏幕区域的横向模式", "minLevel": 0, "maxLevel": 10000, "category": "lifeup", "priority": 0, "postState": 1, "tags": "触摸"}, {"id": 53, "createdAt": "2022-06-14T09:58:44", "updatedAt": "2025-01-16T05:29:50", "langCode": "zh", "appName": "Nice Catch", "shortDescription": "您是否曾在没有收到通知的情况下经历过设备的任何振动？ 查看原因不明的操作（如振动或屏幕打开）的原因。", "pkgName": "com.samsung.android.app.goodcatch", "thumbnails": ["https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-134fc4.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-3712ff.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-b795ed.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-c6d267.png"], "title": "检查设备上原因不明的操作的原因。", "description": "- 可用项目\n：振动、铃声模式、通话模式、Toast 弹出窗口、广告屏幕、屏幕打开、设置更改、媒体音量静音", "minLevel": 0, "maxLevel": 10000, "category": "lifeup", "priority": 0, "postState": 1, "tags": "通知;设置"}, {"id": 57, "createdAt": "2022-06-14T10:01:29", "updatedAt": "2025-01-16T05:32:22", "langCode": "zh", "appName": "One Hand Operation +", "shortDescription": "只需拇指即可轻松使用手机或平板电脑。在屏幕的左右侧屏幕添加了一个小小的处理程序，这样就可以单手使用设备，您还可以配置常用功能以对应特定手势并立即激活它们。", "pkgName": "com.samsung.android.sidegesturepad", "thumbnails": ["https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-06-15-0e4665.jpeg", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-06-15-4e23d0.jpeg", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-06-15-502345.jpeg", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-06-15-61cbb7.jpeg", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-06-15-7f4a4c.jpeg", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-06-15-82a952.jpeg", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-06-15-9bc3f7.jpeg", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-06-15-af9201.jpeg"], "title": "只需拇指即可轻松使用您的设备！", "description": "- 配置水平/对角向上/对角向下方向的手势功能\n- 通过手势直接激活常用功能，如返回、主屏幕和最近使用的应用程序\n- 更改手势滑动位置并添加对应功能", "minLevel": 0, "maxLevel": 10000, "category": "lifeup", "priority": 0, "postState": 1, "tags": "手势;多窗口"}, {"id": 59, "createdAt": "2022-06-14T10:03:00", "updatedAt": "2025-01-16T05:29:29", "langCode": "zh", "appName": "日常程序+", "shortDescription": "Bixby Routines 中添加了各种功能，可以让您新建功能更强大的日常程序。在 Bixby Routines 中尝试 Routine+ 的额外功能。", "pkgName": "com.samsung.android.app.routineplus", "thumbnails": ["https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-06a857.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-690594.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-959d87.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-c69fa7.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2022-07-01-d24ff3.png"], "title": "新建更实用的日常程序。", "description": "- 添加了条件\n ：使用指纹、S Pen 操作、侧面和导航按钮操作进行解锁\n- 添加了动作\n ：文本阅读器、方向键。触控宏\n- 通过推荐的日常程序轻松使用添加的功能\n- 轻松共享二维码并导入保存的日常程序", "minLevel": 0, "maxLevel": 10000, "category": "lifeup", "priority": 0, "postState": 1, "tags": "触摸"}, {"id": 61, "createdAt": "2022-06-14T10:04:27", "updatedAt": "2025-01-16T05:29:10", "langCode": "zh", "appName": "MultiStar", "shortDescription": "体验改进的多窗口。特别是这提供了更加令人愉悦的功能，以便在大屏幕上更好地使用。", "pkgName": "com.samsung.android.multistar", "thumbnails": ["https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2024-11-29-16b8e0.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2024-11-29-2944e5.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2024-11-29-65908a.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2024-11-29-88d59b.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2024-11-29-ee25d8.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2024-11-29-f02458.png"], "title": "体验升级后的多窗口功能。", "description": "<通用>\n- 在多窗口中使用多个应用程序，而无需暂停\n- 运行多窗口时，通过调整大小以适应屏幕来显示更多内容\n- 当应用程序之间的活动更改时，避免最小化弹窗视图\n- 删除分屏视图中的模糊效果（One UI 4 或更高）\n\n<针对 Galaxy Flip>\n- 在外屏中快速启动游戏应用程序或某些媒体应用程序（One UI 4 或更高）\n\n<我 ♡ 折叠屏：针对 Galaxy Fold>\n- 使用 UDC 上的黑色覆盖孔\n- 配置应用程序设置，以在折叠时适应全屏尺寸\n\n<我 ♡ DeX>\n- 无论连接配件如何，均支持高分辨率\n- 同时使用更多应用程序\n- 启动和结束 DeX 模式时自动重启最近使用的应用程序", "minLevel": 0, "maxLevel": 10000, "category": "lifeup", "priority": 0, "postState": 1, "tags": "多窗口"}, {"id": 68, "createdAt": "2022-10-14T02:21:34", "updatedAt": "2025-01-16T05:31:09", "langCode": "zh", "appName": "Camera Assistant", "shortDescription": "根据需求自定设置相机。", "pkgName": "com.samsung.android.app.cameraassistant", "thumbnails": ["https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2023-02-07-76cb9f.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2023-02-07-9c966f.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2023-02-07-a86dc5.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2023-02-07-d2780d.png"], "title": "此应用程序提供以下开/关功能：", "description": "- 自动 HDR\n  在照片和视频的亮处和暗处捕捉更多细节。\n- 对照片进行柔化处理\n  平滑照片模式下照片中的锐利边缘和纹理。\n- 自动切换镜头\n  让相机根据缩放、照明和与拍摄对象的距离来选择最佳镜头。\n- 在照片模式下录制视频\n  长按快门按钮可在照片模式下录制视频。\n- 更快的快门\n  通过捕获更少的帧来加快快门速度。这可能会降低照片质量。\n- 在 HDMI 显示器上进行清晰预览\n  在连接 HDMI 的显示器上显示不带设置或按钮的相机预览。\n\n此应用程序也可以使用以下功能。\n- 采用定时器模式拍摄的照片数量\n- 相机超时", "minLevel": 0, "maxLevel": 10000, "category": "lifeup", "priority": 0, "postState": 1, "tags": "功能扩展"}, {"id": 75, "createdAt": "2022-11-07T00:37:53", "updatedAt": "2025-01-16T05:31:37", "langCode": "zh", "appName": "RegiStar", "shortDescription": "方便地配置设置应用程序, 并快速启动有用的功能。", "pkgName": "com.samsung.android.app.galaxyregistry", "thumbnails": ["https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2023-08-02-1465d3.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2023-08-02-214fe7.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2023-08-02-3ce249.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2023-08-02-869645.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2023-08-02-8f07a9.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2023-08-02-a25564.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2023-08-02-ac5310.png"], "title": "方便地配置家庭设置", "description": "方便地配置设置应用程序，并按下侧键，点击背面，或强烈按下屏幕以快速启动有用的功能。\n\n-重新配置设置主屏菜单\n：更改顺序、隐藏、管理组\n-在设置主屏上显示三星帐户的设置方法\n-搜索设置更改历史记录,更改通知设置\n通过轻敲设备的背面来激活功能\n用长按边键运行特性\n-用力按压屏幕运行特性(Galaxy Fold 4)", "minLevel": 33, "maxLevel": 10000, "category": "lifeup", "priority": 0, "postState": 1, "tags": "设置;触摸"}, {"id": 103, "createdAt": "2025-02-19T05:36:51", "updatedAt": "2025-02-19T06:14:46", "langCode": "zh", "appName": "Display Assistant", "shortDescription": "Display Assistant는 다양한 디스플레이와 관련된 기능의 확장을 제공한다.", "pkgName": "com.samsung.android.displayassistant", "thumbnails": ["https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2025-02-19-1a3d8d.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2025-02-19-27d3c0.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2025-02-19-8338e8.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2025-02-19-91c117.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2025-02-19-9508e4.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2025-02-19-eeea61.png"], "title": "改善您的显示体验", "description": "- 管理每个应用程序的屏幕超时\n- 提供保持屏幕常亮功能\n- 提供亮度限制配置文件功能\n- 管理每个应用程序的刷新率\n- 提供多种自适应亮度选项\n- 提供幕布功能", "minLevel": 35, "maxLevel": 10000, "category": "lifeup", "priority": 0, "postState": 1, "tags": "功能扩展"}, {"id": 110, "createdAt": "2025-03-06T06:46:41", "updatedAt": "2025-03-10T01:47:02", "langCode": "zh", "appName": "Game Booster +", "shortDescription": "与Galaxy一起享受更愉快的游戏体验！", "pkgName": "com.samsung.android.game.honeyplayplus", "thumbnails": ["https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2025-03-06-ef38f7.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2025-03-06-2a1e67.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2025-03-06-efa4aa.png", "https://cdn.goodlocklabs.com/terrace/plugin/2025-03-06-4975d2.png"], "title": "与Galaxy一起享受更愉快的游戏体验！", "description": "- 游戏手柄键重新映射\n : 可以将游戏手柄的键重新映射到其他键。\n- GPU设置（旋转优化/纹理质量）\n : 可以减少Vulkan游戏屏幕旋转中使用的GPU负载，或者更改游戏中使用的纹理质量，以改善图像质量或性能。\n- 更改游戏类别\n：可以将那些虽然是游戏但没有被归类为游戏的应用程序直接更改为游戏类别，从而能够获得设备提供的游戏相关支持。", "minLevel": 35, "maxLevel": 10000, "category": "lifeup", "priority": 0, "postState": 1, "tags": "功能扩展"}]}